\033[1;36m_SNASH_______\033[0m
\033[2msnake in bash \033[0m

\033[1;36m_Gameplay\033[0m
  Goal: Reach the highest score possible.
  Apples: Eat apples for points, but be aware: Leaving them out too long will let them rot and disappear, subtracting points!
  Controls: Move with \033[1mw\033[0m \033[1ma\033[0m \033[1ms\033[0m \033[1md\033[0m (or \033[1mh\033[0m \033[1mj\033[0m \033[1mk\033[0m \033[1ml\033[0m).
  Death: Hitting a wall or your own body.

\033[1;36m_Usage\033[0m
  $0 [options]

\033[1;36m_Arguments\033[0m
  \033[1m-h\033[0m, \033[1m--help\033[0m          Show this help text.
  \033[1m-v\033[0m, \033[1m--version\033[0m       Show game version.
  \033[1m-s\033[0m, \033[1m--scores\033[0m        Show local score history.
  \033[1m-f\033[0m, \033[1m--fullscreen\033[0m    Use terminal size for playfield.
  \033[1m-t\033[0m, \033[1m--in-terminal\033[0m   Fullscreen without initial board rendering.

\033[1;36m_Difficulty\033[0m
  \033[1m-medium\033[0m                Medium mode (default).
  \033[1m-easy\033[0m                  Easy mode.
  \033[1m-hard\033[0m                  Hard mode.
  \033[1m-d <number>=0\033[0m          Custom difficulty value.

